  <sect2 role="installation">
    <title>Installation de libkcddb</title>

    <para>
      Installez <application>libkcddb</application> en lançant les commandes suivantes :
       
    </para>

<screen><userinput>mkdir build &amp;&amp;
cd build &amp;&amp;
cmake -DCMAKE_INSTALL_PREFIX=&kde-dir;       -DSYSCONF_INSTALL_DIR=/etc/kde       .. &amp;&amp;
make</userinput></screen>

    <para>
      Maintenant, en tant qu'utilisateur <systemitem class="username">root</systemitem> :
    </para>

<screen role="root"><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>
  </sect2>

